Privacy Policy

Cooparentive does not collect, sell, or share personal data.

All data entered into the app are stored locally on the user’s device and, if enabled, synced securely via Apple iCloud using CloudKit and Firebase.

The app does not use third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking services.

Coop data is stored securely on a Firebase server, but personal data is never stored.

If you have questions about this privacy policy, you may contact the developer at: sheltodj11@gmail.com
